				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">in no particular order..
<br />

<br />
your planned upgrades 
<br />
1/3/4  are good choices, not to sure of the gloves (doesnt ring a bell)
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Helm</span> get earthweave or ornate( though need to be 56ish for ornate )
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Finger(left)</span> due to your level a Band of Twilight would be very good for ya ( good ring overall decent stats good foci )
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Neck</span> couple things you could do here, 1) (cheap) Black Sapphire necklace / 2) (moderate) Necklace of Flame Marked Links
<br />
3) (expensive) Talisman of the Spiritseer
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Face/mask</span> Mask of Thunder
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Arms</span> Earthweave
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Wrist</span> Earthweave 
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Shoulders</span> terrorclaws hide is nice (i use to use that at your level on old toon)
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Legs</span> Earthweave (if ya cant afford Dreadfangs Hide is relativly cheap a small upgrade though earthweave is a better item overall)
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Primary</span> a Blood Bladed Dagger
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Secondary</span> Tactician's Bulwark<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1014810" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www3.telus.net/cbriere1/rootedxsig.jpg" border="0" /></a>
