				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">At 51, you're well under the recommended level of 63 for Earthweave, but I think you'd like the HPs anyway.
<br />

<br />
Replace white gold necklace with Black Sapphire Velium Necklace.
<br />

<br />
Keep that CoSs handy, but consider questing the Demilich Skullcap.  There is a thread on it in this forum I believe.
<br />

<br />
Replace Bigurdling ring with common 65 HP ring.
<br />

<br />
Replace Gatorscale with some bazaar lewts.
<br />

<br />
Replace Cone of the Mystics with Book of the Lost City (has BA3) or Blood Bladed Dagger.
<br />

<br />
Replace Decaying Bone Idol with Ceramic Skull or Ceramic Gavel.  
<br />

<br />
Find where yoiu are weak with respect to focus items, and do tribute to shore the gaps.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: red"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=135422" target="_blank" class="postlink">ArchLich Antinice</a></span></span>
