				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Thanks for the feedback guys, I really appreciate it.
<br />

<br />
I watched the prices for a few days, and got lucky with a couple of cheaper upgrades.
<br />

<br />
I replaced the <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=8990" target="_blank" class="postlink">Death Mask of Elysians</a> with a <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=32083" target="_blank" class="postlink">Serpentine Mask</a> for 5K.
<br />

<br />
I also replaced the <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=4686" target="_blank" class="postlink">Coldain Skin Gloves</a> with the previously mentioned <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31669[/url" target="_blank" class="postlink">Gloves of Penitence</a> with a net gain of 300 plat after I sold off my CSG.
<br />

<br />
The Band of Twilight looks great because it's a ring slot, but I'm wondering if I might not be better off getting a Ceramic Gavel of Justice.  At 15k vs 8k, the Gavel would be cheaper, is AE4 vs AE3 and is within my means.  I really hate plat farming, to the point I'd rather tradeskill. 
<br />

<br />
The <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30490" target="_blank" class="postlink">Swirling Silk Bracer</a> and <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30483" target="_blank" class="postlink">Earring of Oppression</a> remain on my to get list.
<br />

<br />
